quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  16,88,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe …ďe paddii e laawol Alla ngol, min …ďeydiranii …ďe lepte e hoore lepte, sabu ko …ďe bonniraynoo kon."
  16,89,"(JaŇčto kadi) √Īande minn immintinoyta e kala mofte ko seeditoo e ma…ď…ďe, jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, min ngadda maa [an Muhammadu] ko seeditoo e …ďee …óoo. min njippini e maa…óa deftere nden, ko nde …ďannginoore kala huunde, e peewal, e yurmeende, e welo-welo wonan¬īde juul…ďe …ďen."
  16,90,"Tabitii Alla yamirii nuun…óal, e mo∆ī∆īingol, e mo∆ī∆īagol e joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral. homo ha…óa gaay e pan-kare, e ko a√Īinii, e bewre. homo waajoo on, mbeleejo'o, on mbaajitoray."
  16,91,"kuu…ďnee ahadi Alla ndiin si on ahodaama, wata on pirtu goo…óndooje …óeen …ďaawo …óe tenntineede, gooŇč…óii on mba…óii Alla seedanii…óo [on e hunnugol ngol]. Pellet, ko ganndu…óo ko ngolloton."
  16,92,"Wota on ngon wano (debbo) pirtunoo…óo mottawol mun …ďaawo doole firtude, ho…óon njogitora goo…óndooje mon …óeen jamfondiro hakkunde mon, nde mofte [mon …óen] wonata …ďurde tonaade e dii mofte goo. ngandee Alla no jarribora on …óuum. ma o …ďanngina- na on √Īande darngal, …óuu ko luutondiratno…óon e mum."
  16,93,"Sinno Alla muuyuno, o wa…óatno on mofte goote. Kono, Himo majjina on Mo o muuyi, O feewna on mo O muuyi. ma on lannditoye e …óuu ko ngollatno…óon."